Permissions:

    // TODO: Sort these perms out
    - nChat.commands.muteServer : Allows muting/un-muting of the entire server.
    - nChat.commands.mutePlayer : Allows muting/un-muting of specific players.
    - nChat.muteExempt : Makes the target player/group exempt from global and/or targeted mutes.
    - nChat.emote : Allows the user to do emotes

    // Sorted
    - nchat.commands.puppet : Allows you to send chat from a player.

Death Messages:

    - slain_EntityName : EntityName = Skeleton, VillagerGolem, Player etc.
    - fall : Death from falling
    - suffocation : Death from snu snu
    - drowned : Someone forgot they wern't a fish
    - explosion : TNT, creeper bang, ghast fireball etc
    - lava : Swam in some lava without protection
    - unknown : Server death, command, anvil etc
    - cactus : Got freaky with a cactus
    - fire : Burnt to death or fried by lightning
    - arrow_EntityName : Shot by EntityName IE Skeleton or Player
    - starvation : Ran out of hunger
    - magic : Potions or a wizard did it